  "body": "During discussion and experiments with @chriseth, we found a code that should compile but does not currently:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ cat ext-general.sol \r\ncontract B {\r\n                function f() external {}\r\n}\r\n\r\ncontract D is B {\r\n                function f() {}\r\n}\r\n$ solc/solc ext-general.sol \r\nWarning: This is a pre-release compiler version, please do not use it in production.\r\next-general.sol:1:1: Warning: Source file does not specify required compiler version!\r\ncontract B {\r\n^\r\nSpanning multiple lines.\r\next-general.sol:6:3: Error: Override changes extended function signature.\r\n                function f() {}\r\n                ^-------------^\r\n```",
