    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I assume that the derived `f()` function is meant to be `public` here which was probably a default in earlier versions. With that assumption, the above example works now.\r\n\r\n```\r\ncontract B {\r\n\tfunction f() external virtual {}\r\n}\r\n\r\ncontract D is B {\r\n\tfunction f() public override {}\r\n}\r\n```",
